{
  "stem": "24409.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they left for the border until the border on the Australian-Yugoslav border, where there were-- also Italian border.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Where they had basically because they didn't have any Italian transit visa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The transit visa was given only for the shipping port for that they could really transit just-- there was no ships there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I was punished in Vienna and there were things he told me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You go back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, I was not enthused about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We met in Fiume.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Two people from the Vienna transport who had a [INAUDIBLE] with one of them and somebody else that came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we met in Fiume trying to get a visa from the Italians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Without a ship.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For let's say, put in the meanwhile be out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And a group of about 50, I think, Betarim had at the same time arrived from the Baltic countries to whom we owe this ship.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had some hidden in the basement of a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the ship didn't come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The ship didn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And one day, I had a friend in Athens who had connections there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one day in the morning-- it was in the early morning, I remember-- there was a man calling for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Elegant, a very good looking man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My wife says that he was the best-looking man she ever saw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Very impressive looking man who told me that he is representing the devised group, which was a little lodge underground group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They had smuggled liquor into Germany, into the United States as long as the Prohibition was on, and now they were without work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he said, if you do the-- I said, but we don't have any money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He says, you have 2,000 pounds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I said, I've given them there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
